724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"107268c4610a254152c45fdc870e25dc29dd4fdf","tid":845293,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e9180ead5e6f8f94c6d3b1c532a371ead1e59f","tid":845293,"uid":133375,"like":71,"dislike":7,"score":64,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"支爆=香港經濟起飛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:27:04.000Z","msg":"港英時就係，依家支共一定拖埋香港一齊死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:23:08.000Z","msg":"一爆啲強國人一定好似喪屍咁幾億湧落嚟"},{"pid":"3507a766c563b8827d75613471427d64e3fecd92","tid":845293,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:25:41.000Z","msg":"歷史都係支那愈仆街香港愈好"},{"pid":"415fba6cdc694deeb6f9604a995f56d3d0ea25b9","tid":845293,"uid":24853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"只要全香港既死可以換來支爆及支那滅族<br />\n我願意喎"},{"pid":"087c56f3980b468fa7a75436a4eef1e9be38fcec","tid":845293,"uid":59855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"講咁多野都只係亞媽係女人程度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aef1bfff17c5a16b9427fd88a97969ac213e651","tid":845293,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"爆左一定會拖累香港，反而個經濟不景，增長不再，但大致穩定，香港先會有優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}